<h1>Installing with the Debian-Installer</h1>
 
<p>
<if-stable-release release="etch">
<strong>For official Debian <current_release_etch> installation media and
information</strong>, see
<a href="$(HOME)/releases/etch/debian-installer">the etch page</a>.
</if-stable-release>
<if-stable-release release="lenny">
<strong>For official Debian <current_release_lenny> installation media and
information</strong>, see
<a href="$(HOME)/releases/lenny/debian-installer">the lenny page</a>.
</if-stable-release>
</p>

<p>
All images linked below are for the version of Debian Installer being
developed for the next Debian release and will install Debian testing
(<q><current_testing_name></q>) by default.
</p>

<if-stable-release release="etch">
<p>
